        <item>
            <title>中國網民用爛機殼砌機，內裝 RTX 4090 總值 3 萬成功呃到屋企人</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/12/expensive-diy-parts-in-cheap-box/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=expensive-diy-parts-in-cheap-box</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/12/expensive-diy-parts-in-cheap-box/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 07:00:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[桌上電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[RTX 4090]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[舊機箱]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1219408</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>很多男士們購買貴重電子產品、模型都很難入屋，想盡各式奇招，買 PS4 扮買路由器這個笑話也説了很久。而近日中國就有一名網民，利用殘破不堪的機箱砌機，裡面竟裝有最頂尖顯示卡 GeForce RTX 4090，總值近 3 萬元人民幣，最後這部超強電腦卻能成功「入屋」。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1219413 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/s_b66a73c161904c2c80-343x580.png" alt="" width="343" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/s_b66a73c161904c2c80-343x580.png 343w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/s_b66a73c161904c2c80.png 532w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 343px" /></p><p>根據中國媒體報道，有一個男子給朋友組裝了一部「復古電腦」，外殼所用的膠已嚴重變黃，更有光碟機這種歷史產物。但這個簡陋機箱的裡面，卻裝有總值接近 3 萬元人民幣（約港幣 3.26 萬元）的 DIY 硬件。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1219412 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/s_b135bacd828f47bfac-385x580.png" alt="" width="385" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/s_b135bacd828f47bfac-385x580.png 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/s_b135bacd828f47bfac.png 597w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 385px" /></p><p>一翻開外蓋，就可看到電腦裡面的佈局。一張售價超過 1.2 萬港元起跳的 GeForce RTX 4090 顯示卡，機箱內裝更用上 RGB 裝飾的主機板、記憶體、電源線。不過機箱以簡陋膠蓋覆蓋，不像今時今日的電競電腦有玻璃機蓋，這些 RGB 電競燈飾平時就看不到了。</p><p>網民紛紛稱讚事主的頭貓，指這部電腦「斯是陋室，威武的芯」、「茅台倒礦泉水瓶」。</p><p>其實以前都有中國網民想到用舊機殼裝新機，甚至裝得比今次報道的還勁。大家在砌機時可考慮砌一部這樣外殼的電腦吧&#8230;</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1219410" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz49dazat3csqoq-582x580.jpg" alt="" width="582" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz49dazat3csqoq-582x580.jpg 582w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz49dazat3csqoq.jpg 903w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz49dazat3csqoq-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 582px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1219411" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz4penzbt3csu0u-579x580.jpg" alt="" width="579" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz4penzbt3csu0u-579x580.jpg 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz4penzbt3csu0u.jpg 898w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/9aqqygz4penzbt3csu0u-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 579px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.workercn.cn/c/2024-02-07/8145089.shtml">中工網</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/29/rtx-4090-d/wireless-home/desktop-pc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NVIDIA 中國推降級版 RTX 4090 D    價錢一樣但效能較慢</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/19/geforce-rtx-4090-removed-from-official-nvidia-china-websit/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">美國 GeForce RTX 4090 禁令生效　Nvidia 中國官網刪除所有相關資料</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/12/expensive-diy-parts-in-cheap-box/fun-tech/">中國網民用爛機殼砌機，內裝 RTX 4090 總值 3 萬成功呃到屋企人</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
